---
import storyImage from "../assets/volunteer-v3.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#FAF7F2] py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6">
    <div class="grid items-end gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.08fr_0.92fr] lg:gap-16">
      <img
        src={storyImage.src}
        alt="A Children First volunteer sharing a learning moment"
        class="h-[520px] w-full rounded-[2rem] object-cover sm:h-[700px] lg:rounded-[3rem]"
      />

      <div class="pb-0 lg:pb-10">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#D97706] sm:text-sm">
          Our Story
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#1F2937] sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
          A foundation shaped by real relationships.
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-8 text-[#1F2937]/70 md:text-xl md:leading-9">
          Our work happens in classrooms, community spaces and everyday conversations where children are encouraged to ask questions, try again and feel known. The change we seek is not distant or abstract. It begins when one child feels supported enough to imagine more.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
